				<description>&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;img-fluid &#34;&#xA;            src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/pixis-new-ios-app-turns-text-messages-into-interactive-ar-experiences-2800x1470.png&#34;&#xA;             srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/pixis-new-ios-app-turns-text-messages-into-interactive-ar-experiences-576x302.webp 576w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/pixis-new-ios-app-turns-text-messages-into-interactive-ar-experiences-768x403.webp 768w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/pixis-new-ios-app-turns-text-messages-into-interactive-ar-experiences-992x521.webp 992w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/pixis-new-ios-app-turns-text-messages-into-interactive-ar-experiences-1200x630.webp 1200w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/pixis-new-ios-app-turns-text-messages-into-interactive-ar-experiences-1400x735.webp 1400w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/pixis-new-ios-app-turns-text-messages-into-interactive-ar-experiences-2800x1470.webp 2800w&#34; sizes=&#34;100vw&#34; height=&#34;1470&#34; width=&#34;2800&#34; alt=&#34;Featured Image&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;introduction-to-pixis-innovative-approach&#34; class=&#34;heading &#34;&gt;Introduction to Pixi&amp;rsquo;s Innovative Approach&lt;a href=&#34;#introduction-to-pixis-innovative-approach&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;introduction-to-pixis-innovative-approach&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-link anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; --&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;svg-inline--fa fas fa-link anchor&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; role=&#34;img&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 576 512&#34;&gt;&lt;use href=&#34;#fas-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&amp;nbsp;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The world of messaging has undergone significant transformations over the years, from simple text messages to the use of stickers, GIFs, and emoji reactions. However, Pixi, a pioneering company in the tech industry, is now betting on the next evolution of messaging: interactive augmented reality (AR). This novel approach promises to redefine how we interact with each other through our mobile devices. In this article, we will delve into the details of Pixi&amp;rsquo;s new iOS app, exploring its features, potential impact, and what this means for the future of messaging.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
